title: Rubrik acquires Predibase to accelerate adoption of AI agents
content: Predibase helps companies train and fine-tune open source AI models which will help Rubrik customers deploy AI agents faster.

title: Anthropic just made every Claude user a no-code app developer
content: Anthropic transforms Claude AI into a no-code app development platform with 500 million user-created artifacts, intensifying competition with OpenAI's Canvas feature as AI companies battle for developer supremacy.

title: Google unveils Gemini CLI an open-source AI tool for terminals
content: Google is launching a new agentic AI tool that will put its Gemini AI models closer to where developers are already coding. The company announced on Wednesday the launch of Gemini CLI, an agentic AI tool designed to run locally from your terminal.

title: Google's new AI will help researchers understand how our genes work
content: Google's DeepMind division says it's made a leap in trying to understand the genetic code with AlphaGenome, an AI model that can predict how genes work from their DNA sequence.

title: Stanford's ChatEHR allows clinicians to query patient medical records using natural language without compromising patient data
content: ChatEHR accelerates chart reviews for ER admissions, streamlines patient transfer summaries and synthesizes complex medical histories.
